Invocation Name: robert downey quotes
des: Robert Downey Jr. Aka Iron Man is such an inspiring personality. He's seen the worst of times when he was broke and the absolute surreal times when he was on top. This skill will help you get deeper into the way RDJ thinks and lives his life. Of course besides being the Genius, Billionaire, Playboy, Philantropist. The quotes are all his and they are extremely inspiring, motivating, and humorous too. We'd suggest you to add this skill as a part of your good morning routine. So, that when you say Alexa, Good Morning, RDJ quotes are the first thing you hear and they motivate you for the rest of the day.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
